2018年9月2日，[[索马里|索马里]][[摩加迪休|摩加迪休]]发生了[[自殺攻擊|自杀式]][[汽车炸弹|汽车炸弹袭击]]。<ref name="BBC article">{{Cite web|title=School hit in huge Somali explosion|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-45387620|accessdate=2018-09-04|date=2018-09-02|work=BBC News|language=en-GB|archive-date=2021-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210117162611/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-45387620|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="CNN article">{{Cite web|title=At least 6 dead in car bombing in Somalia's capital|url=https://www.cnn.com/2018/09/02/africa/mogadishu-somalia-car-bombing-intl/index.html|accessdate=2018-09-04|author=Omar Nor|date=2018-09-02|work=CNN|archive-date=2020-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201118144007/https://www.cnn.com/2018/09/02/africa/mogadishu-somalia-car-bombing-intl/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 事件 ==
2018年9月2日，一辆汽车在政府办公室附近被军事人员拦截后引爆，造成包括在场的3名士兵在内的至少6人死亡，另有14人受伤。<ref name="Deutsche Welle">{{Cite web|title=Mogadishu suicide bombing kills children and soldiers|url=https://www.dw.com/en/mogadishu-suicide-bombing-kills-children-and-soldiers/a-45326900|accessdate=2018-09-04|author=(http://www.dw.com)|date=2018-09-02|first=Deutsche Welle|work=DW.COM|language=en|archive-date=2020-09-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200917010838/https://www.dw.com/en/mogadishu-suicide-bombing-kills-children-and-soldiers/a-45326900|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="BBC article"/>这起事件还造成附近一所学校倒塌，附近房屋受损，一座[[清真寺|清真寺]]屋顶被炸毁，目标建筑也被摧毁。<ref name="aljazeera">{{Cite web|title=Somalia: Suicide bomb attack hits offices and school in Mogadishu|url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2018/09/deadly-suicide-blast-hits-somalia-mogadishu-180902073922769.html|accessdate=2018-09-05|date=2018-09-02|work=www.aljazeera.com|archive-date=2020-09-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200916223432/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2018/09/deadly-suicide-blast-hits-somalia-mogadishu-180902073922769.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 反应 ==
袭击发生后不久，[[伊斯兰主义|伊斯兰]]激进组织[[青年党_(索马里)|青年党]]宣称对这次袭击负责。<ref name="BBC article"/><ref name="CNN article"/>该组织经常用炸弹袭击首都，曾于[[2017年10月摩加迪沙恐怖袭击|2017年10月卡车炸弹袭击]]中炸死587人。<ref name="TimesDaily">{{Cite web|title=Suicide car bombing in Somalia's capital kills at least 6|url=https://www.timesdaily.com/news/nation/suicide-car-bombing-in-somalia-s-capital-wounds-at-least/article_156cacf0-938a-5805-8407-008ffb6eaae5.html|accessdate=2018-09-04|author=Press|date=2018-09-02|first=ABDI GULED Associated|work=TimesDaily|language=en}}</ref>

